@node perfect hash generator
@subsection Perfect Hash Generator
@cindex Perfect Hash Generator

@file{make-host-2.lisp} uses the Perfect Hash Generator
extensively. This is loaded using the following command defined in
@file{shared.lisp}

@example
(preload-perfect-hash-generator
 (perfect-hash-generator-journal :input))
@end example





